  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not sure what he's been doing the night before, Chris wakes up in a strange room, handcuffed to a pipe. He doesn't recognize the girl that wakes up next to him, but it seems they're both in a similar predicament.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What's their story? Can they get out?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228600/extras/e5b437fec4a0e99a0b1b8b569331d065.webp?t=1733518733\" width=280 height=44 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2-3 hours  for a single playthrough (6-8 hours for all endings)</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7 endings (6 main + 1 secret one)</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choices that affect Chris' state of mind and his relationship with Beryl</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Escape room puzzles (point-and-click sections)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A story-rich, character-driven narrative</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Optional free adult text patch</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228600/extras/fbced8d1c723f8a2fe880b714c1c5b77.webp?t=1733518733\" width=280 height=44 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Nayru</strong> - Creator<br><strong>Xolf</strong> - Co-writing / Coding Assistance <br><strong>OddTillTheEnd</strong> - Music</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not sure what he's been doing the night before, Chris wakes up in a strange room, handcuffed to a pipe. He doesn't recognize the girl that wakes up next to him, but it seems they're both in a similar predicament.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What's their story? Can they get out?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228600/extras/e5b437fec4a0e99a0b1b8b569331d065.webp?t=1733518733\" width=280 height=44 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2-3 hours  for a single playthrough (6-8 hours for all endings)</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7 endings (6 main + 1 secret one)</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choices that affect Chris' state of mind and his relationship with Beryl</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Escape room puzzles (point-and-click sections)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A story-rich, character-driven narrative</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Optional free adult text patch</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228600/extras/fbced8d1c723f8a2fe880b714c1c5b77.webp?t=1733518733\" width=280 height=44 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Nayru</strong> - Creator<br><strong>Xolf</strong> - Co-writing / Coding Assistance <br><strong>OddTillTheEnd</strong> - Music</p>",
